<item>
            <title>[SPARK-26538] Postgres numeric array support</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SPARK-26538</link>
                <project id="12315420" key="SPARK">Spark</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Consider the following table definition:&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-sql&quot;&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;create&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;table&lt;/span&gt; test1
(
&#160; &#160;v&#160; &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;numeric&lt;/span&gt;[],
&#160; &#160;d&#160; &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;numeric&lt;/span&gt;
);

&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;insert&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;into&lt;/span&gt; test1 &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;values&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;{1111.222,2222.332}&apos;&lt;/span&gt;, 222.4555);
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;When reading the table into a Dataframe, I get the following schema:&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;root
&#160;|-- v: array (nullable = true)
&#160;|&#160; &#160; |-- element: decimal(0,0) (containsNull = true)
&#160;|-- d: decimal(38,18) (nullable = true)&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Notice that for both columns precision and scale were not specified, but in case of the array element I got both set to 0, while in the other case defaults were set.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Later, when I try to read the Dataframe, I get the following error:&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;java.lang.IllegalArgumentException: requirement failed: Decimal precision 4 exceeds max precision 0
&#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; at scala.Predef$.require(Predef.scala:224)
&#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; at org.apache.spark.sql.types.Decimal.set(Decimal.scala:114)
&#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; at org.apache.spark.sql.types.Decimal$.apply(Decimal.scala:453)
&#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; at org.apache.spark.sql.execution.datasources.jdbc.JdbcUtils$$anonfun$16$$anonfun$apply$6$$anonfun$apply$7.apply(JdbcUtils.scala:474)
&#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; ...&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;


&lt;p&gt;I would expect to get array elements of type decimal(38,18) and no error when reading in this case.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>&lt;p&gt;PostgreSQL 10.4, 9.6.9.&lt;/p&gt;</environment>
